column5: My neighbour just dropped off 6 walleye fillets that he got today, now I'm warming up the frying pan.  we just returned from Florida yesterday and this is a great way to be welcomed home.
Can't beat a friend like that grt... cleaned and ready to fry !
now you gotta get out there and give a gift in return!
Hi Connie, Kim is away at trade school doing his last stint prior to finishing his plumbing apprenticeship. It was the guys who live next to Kim.

thats great...i give a lot of fish to my neighbour too....he does small plumbing jobs for me in return...good set up.   Come on Grt!, yuour sat rught next to red lake...you should be killin 'em....lol...
